# CLIP ChangeLog for app-arch/tar

*tar-1.26-r5 (09 Nov 2015)

  09 Nov 2015; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +tar-1.26-r5.ebuild, -tar-1.26-r4.ebuild:
  Build fix for the 4.4.2 specfile.

*tar-1.26-r4 (03 Nov 2015)

  03 Nov 2015; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +tar-1.26-r4.ebuild, -tar-1.26-r3.ebuild:
  Fix generated RDEPEND.

*tar-1.26-r3 (22 Oct 2015)

  22 Oct 2015; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +tar-1.26-r3.ebuild, -tar-1.26-r2.ebuild:
  Install on the admin and audit jails too.
  Fix libexecdir installation path for RM.

*tar-1.26-r2 (21 Feb 2014)

  21 Feb 2014; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +tar-1.26-r2.ebuild, -tar-1.26-r1.ebuild:
  Missing dependency to autotools eclass in ebuild.

*tar-1.26-r1 (20 Dec 2012)

  20 Dec 2012; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +tar-1.26-r1.ebuild, -tar-1.26.ebuild, +files/tar-1.26-no-gets.patch:
  Fix build against glibc 2.16.

